```

## Completion Criteria

**Signal REFACTOR_COMPLETE** when:
1. All findings in refactor-findings.md have been addressed
2. Build passes (no type errors, no lint errors)
3. Tests pass
4. No dead code or unused imports remain

**Signal CHUNK_DONE** when:
- A meaningful chunk is complete
- More findings remain in refactor-findings.md

**Signal REQUIRES_INPUT** only as last resort:
- Genuinely blocked
- Need human decision on design direction or scope
- Exhausted all other avenues

